{"tid":98081,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好懷念十幾歲果陣","createTime":"2017-01-28T06:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T07:29:48.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81eb5105c82b88ea5fd99b616ad3e83b2e0c4a7b","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5d5089a10f3ef27ffbd307f122ee3c5d8de81d","tid":98081,"uid":52940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"做小朋友時恨做大人，做大人時想變返小朋友，冇咁多野煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcccf4586f1a95d0304588ed1ce5f4221b64ff30","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做小朋友時恨做大人，做大人時想變返小朋友，冇咁多野煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我細個又冇乜諗過想做大人<br />\n亦好似冇點諗過自己大個之後會點<br />\n<br />\n而家又唔想老 但又唔想細<br />\n細個 十幾歲果陣 屋企唔係窮 不過唔會俾咁多零用錢 但果陣冇乜物慾 冇咩想買<br />\n而家想買但冇錢"},{"pid":"762f4ab96e2ab6dea5b8bdc3eb2c4d92e1740016","tid":98081,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"2003年果時"},{"pid":"886adfe77c3a3d51361a37c11d9d463f55510bc3","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2003年果時</blockquote><br />\n你邊年出世<br />\n03年我得8歲<br />\n不過我其實好懷念01-03<br />\n<br />\n04開始俾學校的人蝦"},{"pid":"a0a0a0aca015b9e56a4f7f9cac4004cf1f6630db","tid":98081,"uid":52940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:05:03.000Z","msg":"中學時代最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdd2bcc5106925e264fae99f48605acccd41555","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學時代最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好大壓力 讀書 其他野都係"},{"pid":"172853ea55616cb90bd9c2478c035af367e21aa0","tid":98081,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2003年果時</blockquote><br />\n你邊年出世<br />\n03年我得8歲<br />\n不過我其實好懷念01-03<br />\n<br />\n04開始俾學校的人蝦</blockquote><br />\n幫你講..."},{"pid":"57139311b81d369bac0f67a0b815524b7fb269bd","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2003年果時</blockquote><br />\n你邊年出世<br />\n03年我得8歲<br />\n不過我其實好懷念01-03<br />\n<br />\n04開始俾學校的人蝦</blockquote><br />\n幫你講...</blockquote><br />\n我成世人最純真應該係01-03"},{"pid":"9f85277180990963e3d22a93def44b4bca69ed9e","tid":98081,"uid":52940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中學時代最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好大壓力 讀書 其他野都係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n瘋狂打波，冇理學業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99162ef24a8920eb3c2ddb2f59c77fc7e5c67a52","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中學時代最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好大壓力 讀書 其他野都係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n瘋狂打波，冇理學業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前班男仔打完波入黎開大個冷氣<br />\n<br />\n呢種日子真係回不去了"},{"pid":"3c6560b3151ac8819bfafeebeee80b7d8f1fb45f","tid":98081,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"一定係啦細個邊有咁多野諗。最多諗考試。<br />\n時間都過得慢好多。<br />\n大個就論前途。事業，買樓， 結婚，生仔。<br />\n對於唔係一帆風順班人係難事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df37b2682a5a92429f558320698da483684303f6","tid":98081,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係啦細個邊有咁多野諗。最多諗考試。<br />\n時間都過得慢好多。<br />\n大個就論前途。事業，買樓， 結婚，生仔。<br />\n對於唔係一帆風順班人係難事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前同朋友食飯都變晒講前途同繼唔繼續讀書同埋錢<br />\n<br />\n真係有人咁一帆風順? <br />\n有 生得又靚 又高又瘦又白 把聲又好聽 以前中學又有成班朋友<br />\n佢又有錢去左外國讀書"}]}